== Base templates ==

First create base:

rails app_name -m rails_templates/base.rb

Apply other (optional) templates:

cd app_name
rake rails:template LOCATION=../rails_templates/auth.rb
rake rails:template LOCATION=../rails_templates/twitter.rb
rake rails:template LOCATION=../rails_templates/facebook.rb

== Incompatibilities: ==

* twitter autentication/restful_authentication
The twitter app generates ... [more info needed]

	class User < TwitterAuth::GenericUser

